00:19:50.350 --> 00:19:52.330
The partnership between
Acumen and Google

00:19:52.330 --> 00:19:56.660
goes a long way certainly, both
with financial funding as well

00:19:56.660 --> 00:20:00.940
as office locations and so on.

00:20:00.940 --> 00:20:02.440
And I know that a
bunch of Googlers

00:20:02.440 --> 00:20:04.480
have also worked on
some of these projects,

00:20:04.480 --> 00:20:07.690
including working with
LaborNet, et cetera.

00:20:07.690 --> 00:20:10.060
What message would you
